<title>Game of Life - Simple Version</title>
<indexterm><primary>Game of Life - Simple Version</primary></indexterm>
<section xml:id="_index_1intro_sec">
<title>Introduction</title>

<para>This program is a simple implementation of Conway&apos;s Game of Life, a cellular automaton simulation. It evolves according to certain rules based on the initial configuration of cells.</para>
</section>
<section xml:id="_index_1usage_sec">
<title>Usage</title>

<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>Compile: gcc -o game_of_life game_of_life.c</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>Run: ./game_of_life </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</section>
